## "source" model
| Property | Definition | Value type | Repeatable |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| value | String describing the value source. | String | No |
| code | Code representing the value source. | String | No |
| uri | URI for the value source. | String | No |
| note | Other information related to the value source. Note types must be from the "note" controlled list. | Object ("description" model) | Yes |
| version | The version of the value source. | String | No |
